{"id":30268044,"board_id":260506,"workflow_stage_id":2028806,"version":15,"deleted_at":null,"name":"[EPIC] Promo Card Filtering","recurring_schedule":null,"reminders_schedule":null,"description":"<p>As sports are slowly coming back, I think we need to get a very basic Sports / Casino filter set up on the promo page.</p><p><br></p><p>The RAF should sit in sports to ensure we have something there.</p><p><br></p><p>I guess we should have the filters like:</p><p><br></p><p>All (default) / Casino / Sports / Active</p><p><br></p><p>We can talk about further filters at a later date but I think it’s really important to get this basic step live.</p><p><br></p><p>It might be worth a chat with some techies as to how best we can make that work from the CMS.</p><p>Perhaps we add the filter in the Package Criteria: <a href=\"https://admin2.sportsia.com/index.cfm?section=arawContentEditCriteria&amp;promoContentCriteriaID=3216&amp;promoContentPackageID=3257\"></a><a href=\"https://admin2.sportsia.com/index.cfm?section=arawContentEditCriteria&amp;promoContentCriteriaID=3216&amp;promoContentPackageID=3257\">https://admin2.sportsia.com/index.cfm?section=arawContentEditCriteria&amp;promoContentCriteriaID=3216&amp;promoContentPackageID=3257</a></p><p><br></p><p>There is also a requirement from Melissa relating to Cards appearing in more than one category and the need for a Poker category:</p><p><br></p><p>\"Just wanted to mention that we’ll need to allow for bonuses that should appear for both sports &amp; casino i.e. the current Untracked signup offer is both sports &amp; casino and we are in the process of adding a casino bonus to RAF too. I’d want them to appear under the Sports, Casino and All categories.</p><p><br></p><p>We are also looking into adding a poker first deposit bonus so might want to eventually consider a Poker category too – it would be much lower priority though as deposits made via the poker cashier don’t seem to be flagged as deposits in some of our systems so that might be a bigger project than we want to spend time on for poker at the moment.\"</p><p><br></p>","position":3,"priority":0,"tags":"","created_at":"2020-05-12T17:15:13.000+01:00","updated_at":"2020-06-17T14:08:10.000+01:00","board_version":21186,"archived_at":"2020-06-17T14:08:10.000+01:00","assigned_user_id":262362,"comments_count":2,"size_estimate":"1.0","card_type_id":6839917,"subtasks_count":0,"subtasks_completed_count":0,"attachments_count":0,"custom_field_1":"262362","custom_field_2":null,"custom_field_3":null,"custom_field_4":null,"custom_field_5":null,"custom_field_6":null,"custom_field_7":null,"custom_field_8":null,"custom_field_9":null,"custom_field_10":null,"custom_field_11":null,"custom_field_12":null,"custom_field_13":null,"custom_field_14":null,"custom_field_15":null,"external_link":"https://www.figma.com/file/9oejsxeJcfB0XQmDJGGN51/Filters?node-id=0%3A1","due_date":null,"postponed_until":null,"swimlane_id":611530,"external_id":null,"subtask_search_tags":null,"block_reason":null,"created_by_id":261430,"time_estimate":null,"timers_total":null,"timers_total_updated_at":"2020-06-17T14:08:10.000+01:00","timers_active_count":0,"timers_listed_count":0,"timers_postponed_count":0,"linked_tasks":null,"linked_tasks_status":null,"linked_from":null,"card_color":"yellow","card_color_in_rgb":"#FFEB3B","card_color_invert":false,"size_estimate_description":"1.0 - the same as most of other tasks","search_tags":["[EPIC] Promo Card Filtering","Bonus Opt-in","Richie","262362"],"collaborators":[{"id":262316,"name":"Avid","initials":" A","is_suspended":false,"active":true},{"id":262334,"name":"Alan Butler","initials":" AB","is_suspended":false,"active":true},{"id":262332,"name":"Aidan Haran","initials":" AH","is_suspended":false,"active":true},{"id":262336,"name":"Andrej Neprokin","initials":" AN","is_suspended":true,"active":null},{"id":262354,"name":"Claudio Andrade","initials":" Claudio","is_suspended":true,"active":null},{"id":262356,"name":"Dylan Gaul","initials":" D